I've been sitting at the computer for too long, and I'm tired of the glare when the light hits my laptop. 
I searched for a solution and found an international website https://www.tintfit.com/shop/reflective-window-film, where they sold special windows for both large and small homes. 
I decided to purchase one for myself so I wouldn't be blinded by the light anymore. Now I enjoy the comfort and the nice view from the window.
